      <title>黄金上涨并不完全是通胀爆发：沃顿商学院的西格尔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/gold-rally-not-totally-inflation-flare-wharton-s-siegel-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宾夕法尼亚大学沃顿商学院名誉金融学教授杰里米·西格尔表示，经济的强劲正在推动大宗商品价格上涨，就像彭博电视上的通胀压力一样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/gold-rally-not-totally-inflation-flare-wharton-s-siegel-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 20:27:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Tiger Global 在棘手的风险投资环境中筹集了 22 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/tiger-global-gathers-2-2b-in-tricky-vc-environment-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，老虎环球管理公司为其最新风险投资基金募集了约 22 亿美元，远低于 60 亿美元的目标，也是大约十年来最小的筹款额。 Hema Parma 还有更多。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/tiger-global-gathers-2-2b-in-tricky-vc-environment-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 19:57:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Citadel 的肯·格里芬 (Ken Griffin) 认为增长“温和”，并对美国债务发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/citadel-s-ken-griffin-sees-modest-growth-warns-on-us-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Citadel 创始人肯·格里芬 (Ken Griffin) 告诉投资者，他预计未来几个季度的经济将温和增长，并称美国国债是“一个不容忽视的日益令人担忧的问题”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/citadel-s-ken-griffin-sees-modest-growth-warns-on-us-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 19:34:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃顿商学院的西格尔表示，股市牛市尚未结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/stock-market-bull-run-isn-t-over-wharton-s-siegel-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宾夕法尼亚大学沃顿商学院名誉金融学教授杰里米·西格尔（Jeremy Siegel）表示，美国经济的强劲将导致利率坚挺，但彭博电视台表示，股市的牛市“还有更多的路要走”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/stock-market-bull-run-isn-t-over-wharton-s-siegel-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 19:33:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥将停止部分石油出口，挤压全球市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/mexico-to-halt-some-oil-exports-further-squeezing-global-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥国有石油公司计划在未来几个月内停止部分原油出口，此举将减少全球市场紧缩带来的供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/mexico-to-halt-some-oil-exports-further-squeezing-global-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 18:16:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安德烈蒂的 SPAC 交易带来的现金微乎其微，股价暴跌 58%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/andretti-s-ai-spac-deal-brings-little-cash-as-shares-tumble-54</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人工智能初创公司 ZapataComputingHoldingsInc. 与前印地赛车车手迈克尔·安德雷蒂 (Michael Andretti) 的空白支票公司合并后，尽管绝大多数公众投资者对这笔交易持放弃态度，但该公司首次上市后股价暴跌 58%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/andretti-s-ai-spac-deal-brings-little-cash-as-shares-tumble-54</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:21:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>强劲的 ISM 数据推动 6 月美联储降息几率降至 50% 以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/treasury-yields-extend-climb-after-strong-ism-factory-gauges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员预计美联储今年将减少货币政策宽松——并简单地将 6 月份首次行动的可能性设定为低于 50%——美国制造业活动指标显示自 2022 年以来首次出现扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/treasury-yields-extend-climb-after-strong-ism-factory-gauges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 14:36:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美联储削减赌注的消退，股市与债券一起下跌：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/asian-stocks-set-to-gain-as-fed-awaits-more-data-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[坚实的美国工厂数据强化了美联储将不急于降息的猜测，华尔街交易员导致股票和债券双双走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/asian-stocks-set-to-gain-as-fed-awaits-more-data-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 22:04:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
